review_blob: Citrus, spruce, mocha all you can ask for in a IPA. This is up there with the Double Jack, Hercules, Big A IPA and Shipwrecked if like those you will love this!! Stay thirsty my freinds
If you like stouts this is a must drink!! Lots of flavor perfect balance you cant go wrong with this one!! desert in a bottle!! Caramel, chocolate, vanilla smooth!!!
If you like IPAs and dont like this then check your taste buds!! Perfect balance of what makes a Hall of fame IPA!! Pine yup, mocha yup, smooth yup. If you see this try it and be satisfied!!
beer_name: Great Divide Hercules Double IPA - Barrel Aged

review_blob: Great double IPA has a mocha finish and gets better with each sip!! This is not for the faint of heart! has that great IPA flavor and you wont be disappointed!! Top 5 IPA hands down!!
This beer has it all full body, crisp clean flavor, great after taste and leaves you wanting more!! Man up and enjoy!!
